### .NET Build & Cache ###
# Folders for build outputs and temporary files. This is the most important section.
[Bb]in/
[Oo]bj/
.vs/
.idea/

### IDE & User-Specific ###
# Settings specific to a user's machine or IDE.
*.user
*.suo
*.userosscache
*.sln.docstates

# For VS Code, ignore all user settings except for shared team configurations.
.vscode/*
!.vscode/settings.json
!.vscode/tasks.json
!.vscode/launch.json
!.vscode/extensions.json

### Runtime Data & Logs ###
# Files generated when the application runs. These are not source code.
logs/
*.log
*.binlog

# The workflow engine's JSON "database". This is runtime data.
workflow-definitions.json
workflow-instances.json
*.workflow.json

### Local Configuration ###
# Configuration files that may contain secrets or local machine paths.
appsettings.Development.json
*.Development.json
.env*

### OS-Generated Files ###
# Common files generated by Windows, macOS, and Linux that don't belong in a repo.
Thumbs.db
ehthumbs.db
.DS_Store
._*